Text:
This is the biggest bullshit ever created. Everything that is stated here is totally wrong. I guarantee!

The uploader is a former staff member of SceneHD that got greedy and wanted money for uploading torrents and beiing a staff member. Therefore he got kicked out of SceneHD. The amount of money that is said here is now used on a new server, well spent if you ask me.

Don't trust this, it's just BS!
